        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 10 at 3:05PM CDT by NWS Lake Charles LA</headline>
        <description>At 305 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Harmony, or near Mittie, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to vegetation and outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Oakdale, Oberlin, Mittie, Allen Parish Airport, Bond, and Harmony.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
